metadata.name: #01 "Let's hold hands!!"
metadata.description:
海を超えた先、何があるかわからなかった...
超えた先を知りたく、時に恐れ、意見を共存できず、そして戦った...
けどそれは昔の話
手を繋ごう
今は互いに知ることができ、意見も共有できて、恐れる必要はない

※この作品の売上は手数料など一部を除き全てウクライナへの支援のため寄付させていたします。

We didn't know what lay beyond the sea...
We wanted to know what was beyond, sometimes we were afraid, we could not coexist in our opinions, and we fought...
But that was a long time ago
Let's hold hands.
Now we know each other, we share our opinions, and there is no need to be afraid.

※All proceeds from the sale of this work will be donated to support Ukraine, with the exception of a small portion of commissions.
